"{\"uid\": \"news18.com-olympics-sarabjot-singh-says-he-barely-got-to-train-with-manu-bhaker-before-10m-air-pistol-mixed-event-at-2024-paris-olympics-9026418.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sarabjot Singh, who partnered with Manu Bhaker to win India's first ever Olympic medal in a mixed shooting event, on Saturday said they \\\"barely\\\" got to train together in the run-up to their event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 196, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 46, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Manu Bhaker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Manu_Bhaker\"}, {\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 59, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9996547177514786, \"rank\": 0.00021036897489534485, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bhaker and Sarabjot scripted history with a bronze medal in the 10m air pistol mixed team shooting event at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 198, \"to\": 322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My training was due at 9, hers was due at 12, individually.\", \"from\": 324, \"to\": 384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mixed session lasted for 30 minutes, before which she trained separately, and I separately.\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our conversation was usually brief and limited to 'Apna 100 per cent dena hai (we have to give our 100 per cent)'.\", \"from\": 478, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Apart from that, we enjoyed some banter.\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I would make fun of her, sometimes she would of me,\\\" recalled Sarabjot.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sarabjot also revealed his longtime fandom for Yusuf Dikec and said he has been looking up to the Turkish shooting icon for inspiration since 2011.\", \"from\": 718, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.999988464768332, \"rank\": 1.0720854558239852e-05, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}, {\"begin\": 816, \"end\": 823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"score\": 0.8311489433005949, \"rank\": 0.11567940659208358, \"text\": \"Turkish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turkish_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been watching his (Yusuf's) videos since 2011.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 921, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He has always been like this.\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He is 51 today.\", \"from\": 952, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though I have tried, I could not match his perfection.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I had the chance, I would ask him what he eats?,\\\" said the 22-year-old from Dheen village of Haryana during an interview with PUMA India.\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.999999758052156, \"rank\": 2.3816285390635618e-07, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 1162, \"end\": 1167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9996547177514786, \"rank\": 0.00021036897489534485, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sarabjot said that his pistol is engraved with SSINGH30, comprising his initials and a significant date in his journey.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not give it a name.\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When I achieved my personal best at the 2022 Asian Games in Hangzhou, I got the weapon engraved with 'SSINGH30'.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 0.9999999971605575, \"rank\": 2.7896105544684504e-09, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is my best weapon.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because my medal (gold) came on September 30 and that was a significant achievement,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete also shared that he has had to deal with his fair share of setbacks in his journey.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meditation, and a rare yogic technique called Trataka, helped him.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The main technique is to look at the candle flame with eyes open for three minutes, and then imagine for two minutes.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1833, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I used to keep it directly in front of my eyes.\", \"from\": 1834, \"to\": 1881, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Complete darkness in the room, complete peace, silence.\", \"from\": 1883, \"to\": 1939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My eyes would water; it was not easy.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The most important thing is visualisation in shooting,\\\" said Sarabjot.\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swipe Left For Next Video  In conclusion, the Olympic medallist stated his ambition for the 2028 Los Angeles Games.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"LA '28; iska colour change karna hai (LA '28, I want to change its colour),\\\" said Sarabjot, gesturing toward his glittering bronze medal.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2176, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Sport_Karate_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iska\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Sport_Karate_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Sport_Karate_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 2195, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karna\", \"score\": 0.999999985345312, \"rank\": 1.4654633282278516e-08, \"text\": \"karna\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karna\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Latest Blogs\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": []}]}"